Prop.Name: Desc
Prop.Value: The plant consists of a 5-compartment nitrogen removing activated sludge system: two anoxic tanks followed by three aerobic tanks and a secondary clarifier, in a basic pre-denitrification configuration. Detailed information on the BSM1 and its implementation can be found in Copp (2002).
